flowchart LR
    A[Agent change or prompt update] --> B[Task suite]
    B --> C[Behavior graders]
    C --> D{Regression gate}
    D -->|Pass| E[Ship to production]
    D -->|Fail| F[Debug trace]
    F --> G[Fix prompt, tool policy, or guardrail]
    G --> B
    C --> H[Eval history dashboard]
    H --> I[Release review]

    classDef default fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#94a3b8,color:#1e293b
    classDef gate fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#1f6feb,color:#1e293b
    classDef warn fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,color:#1e293b
    classDef success fill:#ccfbf1,stroke:#0d9488,color:#1e293b

    class D gate
    class F warn
    class E success

